673682,130,2238,49,57,1,65,8,Atha kasmā mahāthero catūsu ariyasaccesu gaṇanaṃ gacchatīti āhāti? 
673683,130,2238,58,60,1,21,2,Saccānaṃ antogadhattā. 
673684,130,2238,61,79,1,123,12,"Yathā hi‘‘ sādhikamidaṃ, bhikkhave, diyaḍḍhasikkhāpadasataṃ anvaddhamāsaṃ uddesaṃ āgacchati, yattha attakāmā kulaputtā sikkhanti. "
673685,130,2238,80,117,1,216,22,"Tisso imā, bhikkhave, sikkhā adhisīlasikkhā adhicittasikkhā adhipaññāsikkhā’’ ti( a. ni.3.88) ettha sādhikamidaṃ diyaḍḍhasikkhāpadasataṃ ekā adhisīlasikkhāva hoti, taṃ sikkhantopi tisso sikkhā sikkhatīti dassito, sikkhānaṃ antogadhattā. "
673686,130,2238,118,139,1,180,20,Yathā ca ekassa hatthipadassa catūsu koṭṭhāsesu ekasmiṃ koṭṭhāse otiṇṇānipi dvīsu tīsu catūsu koṭṭhāsesu otiṇṇānipi siṅgālasasamigādīnaṃ pādāni hatthipade samodhānaṃ gatāneva honti. 
673687,130,2238,140,144,1,43,4,Hatthipadato amuccitvā tasseva antogadhattā. 
673688,130,2238,145,159,1,105,14,Evameva ekasmimpi dvīsupi tīsupi catūsupi saccesu gaṇanaṃ gatā dhammā catūsu saccesu gaṇanaṃ gatāva honti; 
