675124,130,2470,181,195,1,102,13,Siyā nu kho eso maggo {bodhāyā}ti bhaveyya nu kho etaṃ ānāpānassatipaṭhamajjhānaṃ bujjhanatthāya maggoti. 
675125,130,2470,196,216,1,182,18,"Satānusāriviññāṇan ti nayidaṃ bodhāya maggo bhavissati, ānāpānassatipaṭhamajjhānaṃ pana bhavissatīti evaṃ ekaṃ dve vāre uppannasatiyā anantaraṃ uppannaviññāṇaṃ satānusāriviññāṇaṃ nāma. "
