675142,130,2473,93,114,1,143,17,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– paresaṃ viññāpanameva tathāgatassa dhammadesanāya payojanaṃ, tasmā na ekasseva deseti, yattakā viññātāro atthi, sabbesaṃ desetīti. "
675143,130,2473,115,121,1,44,6,Tasmiṃyeva purimasmin ti iminā kiṃ dassetīti? 
675144,130,2473,122,125,1,20,3,Saccako kira cintesi–
675145,130,2473,126,153,1,156,19,"‘‘ samaṇo gotamo abhirūpo pāsādiko suphusitaṃ dantāvaraṇaṃ, jivhā mudukā, madhuraṃ vākkaraṇaṃ, parisaṃ rañjento maññe vicarati, anto panassa cittekaggatā natthī’’ ti. "
675146,130,2473,154,180,1,209,21,"Atha bhagavā, aggivessana, na tathāgato parisaṃ rañjento vicarati, cakkavāḷapariyantāyapi parisāya tathāgato dhammaṃ deseti, asallīno anupalitto ettakaṃ ekavihārī, suññataphalasamāpattiṃ anuyuttoti dassetuṃ evamāha. "
675147,130,2474,2,6,1,32,2,{Ajjhattamevā}ti gocarajjhattameva. 
