675166,130,2476,63,69,1,37,5,Kasmā etassa bhagavā dhammaṃ desesīti? 
675167,130,2476,70,72,1,20,2,Anāgate vāsanatthāya. 
675168,130,2476,73,94,1,157,17,"Passati hi bhagavā,‘‘ imassa idāni upanissayo natthi, mayhaṃ pana parinibbānato samadhikānaṃ dvinnaṃ vassasatānaṃ accayena tambapaṇṇidīpe sāsanaṃ patiṭṭhahissati. "
675169,130,2476,95,117,1,188,20,Tatrāyaṃ kulaghare nibbattitvā sampatte kāle pabbajitvā tīṇi piṭakāni uggahetvā vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā saha paṭisambhidāhi arahattaṃ patvā kāḷabuddharakkhito nāma mahākhīṇāsavo bhavissatī’’ ti. 
675170,130,2476,118,124,1,46,6,Idaṃ disvā anāgate vāsanatthāya dhammaṃ desesi. 
675171,130,2477,2,26,1,275,23,Sopi tattheva tambapaṇṇidīpamhi sāsane patiṭṭhite devalokato cavitvā dakkhiṇagirivihārassa bhikkhācāragāme ekasmiṃ amaccakule nibbatto pabbajjāsamatthayobbane pabbajitvā tepiṭakaṃ buddhavacanaṃ uggahetvā gaṇaṃ pariharanto mahābhikkhusaṅghaparivuto upajjhāyaṃ passituṃ agamāsi. 
675172,130,2477,27,42,1,136,15,Athassa upajjhāyo saddhivihārikaṃ codessāmīti tepiṭakaṃ buddhavacanaṃ uggahetvā āgatena tena saddhiṃ mukhaṃ datvā kathāmattampi na akāsi. 
675173,130,2477,43,50,1,50,6,"So paccūsasamaye vuṭṭhāya therassa santikaṃ gantvā,–"
