675177,130,2477,102,106,1,19,3,"Kiṃ karomi, bhanteti? "
675178,130,2477,107,116,1,90,9,Gaṇaṃ vinodetvā tvaṃ papañcaṃ chinditvā cetiyapabbatavihāraṃ gantvā samaṇadhammaṃ karohīti. 
675179,130,2477,117,131,1,140,14,So upajjhāyassa ovāde ṭhatvā saha paṭisambhidāhi arahattaṃ patvā puññavā rājapūjito hutvā mahābhikkhusaṅghaparivāro cetiyapabbatavihāre vasi. 
