675201,130,2479,42,60,1,122,13,"Yathā, mahārāja , karīsasahassamatte sālikkhette ekasālisīsato avasesasālīyeva bahū, evaṃ mayā kathitaguṇā appā, avasesā bahūti. "
675202,130,2479,61,67,1,32,4,"Aparampi, bhante, upamaṃ karothāti. "
