675213,130,2480,2,3,1,41,2,Papañcasūdaniyā majjhimanikāyaṭṭhakathāya 
675214,130,2481,2,4,1,32,2,Mahāsaccakasuttavaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā.
675215,130,2482,2,4,1,29,2,7 . Cūḷataṇhāsaṅkhayasuttavaṇṇanā 
675216,130,2483,2,13,1,40,5,390. Evaṃ me sutan ti cūḷataṇhāsaṅkhayasuttaṃ. 
675217,130,2483,14,22,1,80,7,Tattha pubbārāme {migāramātupāsāde}ti pubbārāmasaṅkhāte vihāre migāramātuyā pāsāde. 
675218,130,2483,23,51,1,259,23,"Tatrāyaṃ anupubbīkathāatīte satasahassakappamatthake ekā upāsikā padumuttaraṃ bhagavantaṃ nimantetvā buddhappamukhassa bhikkhusaṅghassa satasahassaṃ dānaṃ datvā bhagavato pādamūle nipajjitvā,‘‘ anāgate tumhādisassa buddhassa aggupaṭṭhāyikā homī’’ ti patthanamakāsi. "
675219,130,2483,52,72,1,185,19,Sā kappasatasahassaṃ devesu ceva manussesu ca saṃsaritvā amhākaṃ bhagavato kāle bhaddiyanagare meṇḍakaseṭṭhiputtassa dhanañjayassa seṭṭhino gahe sumanadeviyā kucchimhi paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi. 
675220,130,2483,73,79,1,37,5,Jātakāle cassā {visākhā}ti nāmaṃ akaṃsu. 
675221,130,2483,80,96,1,141,15,"Sā yadā bhagavā bhaddiyanagaraṃ agamāsi, tadā pañcahi dārikāsatehi saddhiṃ bhagavato paccuggamanaṃ katvā paṭhamadassanamhiyeva sotāpannā ahosi. "
675222,130,2483,97,114,1,147,14,"Aparabhāge sāvatthiyaṃ migāraseṭṭhiputtassa puṇṇavaḍḍhanakumārassa gehaṃ gatā, tattha naṃ migāraseṭṭhi mātiṭṭhāne ṭhapesi, tasmā {migāramātā}ti vuccati. "
675223,130,2484,2,9,1,66,7,Patikulaṃ gacchantiyā cassā pitā mahālatāpiḷandhanaṃ nāma kārāpesi. 
675224,130,2484,10,38,1,194,24,"Tasmiṃ piḷandhane catasso vajiranāḷiyo upayogaṃ agamaṃsu, muttānaṃ ekādasa nāḷiyo, pavāḷānaṃ dvāvīsati nāḷiyo, maṇīnaṃ tettiṃsa nāḷiyo, iti etehi ca aññehi ca sattavaṇṇehi ratanehi niṭṭhānaṃ agamāsi. "
675225,130,2484,39,54,1,113,14,"Taṃ sīse paṭimukkaṃ yāva pādapiṭṭhiyā bhassati, pañcannaṃ hatthīnaṃ balaṃ dhārayamānāva naṃ itthī dhāretuṃ sakkoti. "
675226,130,2484,55,72,1,154,17,Sā aparabhāge dasabalassa aggupaṭṭhāyikā hutvā taṃ pasādhanaṃ vissajjetvā navahi koṭīhi bhagavato vihāraṃ kārayamānā karīsamatte bhūmibhāge pāsādaṃ kāresi. 
675227,130,2484,73,83,1,99,9,"Tassa uparibhūmiyaṃ pañca gabbhasatāni honti, heṭṭhābhūmiyaṃ pañcāti gabbhasahassappaṭimaṇḍito ahosi. "
675228,130,2484,84,106,1,128,15,"Sā‘‘ suddhapāsādova na sobhatī’’ ti taṃ parivāretvā pañca dvikūṭagehasatāni, pañca cūḷapāsādasatāni, pañca dīghasālasatāni ca kārāpesi. "
675229,130,2484,107,112,1,42,5,Vihāramaho catūhi māsehi niṭṭhānaṃ agamāsi. 
675230,130,2485,2,23,1,184,19,"Mātugāmattabhāve ṭhitāya visākhāya viya aññissā buddhasāsane dhanapariccāgo nāma natthi, purisattabhāve ṭhitassa ca anāthapiṇḍikassa viya aññassa buddhasāsane dhanapariccāgo nāma natthi. "
675231,130,2485,24,36,1,131,12,So hi catupaññāsakoṭiyo vissajjetvā sāvatthiyā dakkhiṇabhāge anurādhapurassa mahāvihārasadise ṭhāne jetavanamahāvihāraṃ nāma kāresi. 
675232,130,2485,37,46,1,82,8,"Visākhā, sāvatthiyā pācīnabhāge uttamadevīvihārasadise ṭhāne pubbārāmaṃ nāma kāresi. "
675233,130,2485,47,60,1,109,13,Bhagavā imesaṃ dvinnaṃ kulānaṃ anukampāya sāvatthiṃ nissāya viharanto imesu dvīsu vihāresu nibaddhavāsaṃ vasi. 
675234,130,2485,61,75,1,93,12,"Ekaṃ antovassaṃ jetavane vasati, ekaṃ pubbārāme, etasmiṃ pana samaye bhagavā pubbārāme viharati. "
675235,130,2485,76,78,1,11,2,Tena vuttaṃ–
