676153,130,2614,2,13,1,74,8,"{Nappajānātī}ti ettha yasmā nappajānāti, tasmā duppaññoti vuccatīti ayamattho. "
676154,130,2614,14,17,1,18,3,Esa nayo sabbattha. 
676155,130,2614,18,35,1,126,14,"Idaṃ dukkhanti {nappajānātī}ti idaṃ dukkhaṃ, ettakaṃ dukkhaṃ, ito uddhaṃ natthīti dukkhasaccaṃ yāthāvasarasalakkhaṇato na pajānāti. "
676156,130,2614,36,48,1,126,11,Ayaṃ {dukkhasamudayo}ti ito dukkhaṃ samudetīti pavattidukkhapabhāvikā taṇhā samudayasaccanti yāthāvasarasalakkhaṇato na pajānāti. 
676157,130,2614,49,69,1,172,19,Ayaṃ {dukkhanirodho}ti idaṃ dukkhaṃ ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo ca idaṃ nāma ṭhānaṃ patvā nirujjhatīti ubhinnaṃ appavatti nibbānaṃ nirodhasaccanti yāthāvasarasalakkhaṇato na pajānāti. 
676158,130,2614,70,82,1,125,11,Ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī {paṭipadā}ti ayaṃ paṭipadā dukkhanirodhaṃ gacchatīti maggasaccaṃ yāthāvasarasalakkhaṇato na pajānātīti. 
