677245,130,2789,75,81,1,61,6,Paccekabuddhopi bhattakiccāvasāne kukkurassa ekaṃ piṇḍaṃ deti. 
677246,130,2789,82,90,1,75,8,So paccekabuddhe sinehaṃ uppādetvā gopālakena saddhiṃ paṇṇasālampi gacchati. 
