678151,131,42,2,100,1,741,76,"Yena bhagavā {tenupasaṅkamiṃsū}ti santhāgāraṃ niṭṭhitanti sutvā‘‘ gacchāma, naṃ passissāmā’’ ti gantvā dvārakoṭṭhakato paṭṭhāya sabbaṃ oloketvā‘‘ idaṃ santhāgāraṃ devavimānasadisaṃ ativiya manoramaṃ sassirikaṃ kena paṭhamaṃ paribhuttaṃ amhākaṃ dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāya assā’’ ti cintetvā‘‘ amhākaṃ ñātiseṭṭhassa paṭhamaṃ diyyamānepi satthunova anucchavikaṃ, dakkhiṇeyyavasena diyyamānepi satthunova anucchavikaṃ, tasmā paṭhamaṃ satthāraṃ paribhuñjāpessāma, bhikkhusaṅghassa āgamanaṃ karissāma, bhikkhusaṅghe āgate tepiṭakaṃ buddhavacanaṃ āgatameva bhavissati, satthāraṃ tiyāmarattiṃ amhākaṃ dhammakathaṃ kathāpessāma, iti tīhi ratanehi paribhuttaṃ mayaṃ pacchā paribhuñjissāma , evaṃ no dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāya bhavissatī’’ ti sanniṭṭhānaṃ katvā upasaṅkamiṃsu. "
