678156,131,44,15,57,1,462,36,"Sabbapaṭhamaṃ tāva‘‘ gomayaṃ nāma sabbamaṅgalesu vaṭṭatī’’ ti sudhāparikammakatampi bhūmiṃ allagomayena opuñchāpetvā parisukkhabhāvaṃ ñatvā yathā akkantaṭṭhāne padaṃ na paññāyati, evaṃ catujjātiyagandhehi limpāpetvā upari nānāvaṇṇe kaṭasārake santharitvā tesaṃ upari mahāpiṭṭhikakojavake ādiṃ katvā hatthattharaka-assattharaka-sīhattharaka-byagghattharaka-candattharaka-sūriyattharaka-cittattharakādīhi nānāvaṇṇehi attharaṇehi santharitabbakayuttaṃ sabbokāsaṃ santharāpesuṃ. "
